{
  "texts": [
    "With a size of 11.3 billion parameters, it offers significant computational power.",
    "The datasets used to train this LLM are gsm8k, lambada, aqua rat, esnli, quasc, qrec, djaym7/wiki dialog, and qed.",
    "The rationale behind choosing this LLM lies in its suitability for question-answering pipelines in chatbots and its prowess in text-to-text generation tasks.",
    "To implement the chatbot, Google Colab was utilized to write the source code in Python and import the necessary libraries.",
    "Further details on the chatbot implementation are provided in the final phase.4."
  ]
}